phrases: And you feel kind of... sticky.
Armin has not said anything yet!
Cannot you tell just by looking around?
We do not have any more time to waste on him.
Why is Armin the only person left in one piece?
They thought he was a corpse.
It is a pity they ran into a bunch of Eotena,
but why did he have to be the only one to survive?
It just means Eren and the others died in vain.
Want me to shut you up for good?
Our friends are all dying so suddenly.
Once this is all over, marry me!
She is messing around more than usual.
Anyway, you cannot just stay here.
Sorry for the trouble I caused.
I will go join the rear guard.
We have been ordered to advance!
I have just had the wrong perspective this whole time.
A world in which the strong devour the weak.
tried to live strong in this world.
They held out a helping hand to a weakling like me.
I am something that needs protection.
I wanted to live with a strength like theirs.
I wanted to live with them as their equal.
I have given him CPR over and over and over again.
This place is dangerous so let us hurry up and get
We cannot just leave Franz here!
Do not you have any idea what kind of situation we are in?!
That is why I am doing this!
You guys should help too if you want to be saved!
You are supposed to let the people through first!
I am the boss of the trade federation in this town.
Who do you think gives you the food you shit out?
Can you get together the kind of money required to feed all the soldiers here?
This cargo is worth more than you will make in your whole pathetic lives.
You help me and I will help you!
Dad will get all the Eotenas with his cannon.
Do not waste time thinking about it!
We are supposed to be the elite but we still cannot keep up!
What do you think you are doing?
My comrades are dying as we speak.
The noncombatants have not evacuated yet,
so they are fighting the Eotenas and dying.
It is your duty to offer up your hearts to protect us civilians and our wealth!
Do not get all high and mighty just because you parasites have finally emerged from 100 years of uselessness!
If you think it is only natural that people die for others,
then I am sure you will understand.
Sometimes, sacrificing one precious life can save many others.
I have known your boss for a long time.
I can tell him to end you!
But how is a corpse going to tell him anything?
I dulled both my blades in a single attack.
I will be more careful next time.
Seriously, what happened to make you so?
Why am I remembering this now, of all times?

The single-edged blades forged from this metal are widely-known anti-Eotena weapons.

This style of embroidery has been passed down in our family for generations.
You should teach your kids how to do it too.
So how do I get kids?
I-I am not really sure myself.
But look, Dr. Jaeger should be here soon,
She is the same age as you.
There are not any other kids in this area.
So make friends with her, okay?
That attitude is why you have only got one friend.
Did you see a girl around?
I am going to get the Gendarmerie and have them look for her.
You wait for me at the base of the mountain.
You really think she will sell?
We even killed her parents and all.
Take a good look at her face.
Okay, she is fine, but she is just a kid.
I do not care if she is your thing.
In the past, there were different types of humans.
She is the descendent of people who fled into the Walls from a place called the Orient.
We will auction her off to some pervert at the underground market in the capital.
The other Orientals have died out.
She will fetch us quite the price.
Her father did not look Oriental, though.
Her mother was the one who was really worth something!
Why'djya have to freak out and kill her?
I-I did not have a choice!
Unless ya want me to split your head open with this.
I told you to only kill the father!
Do not make this any harder, kid.
How did you find this place?!
I got lost in the forest...
Do not come into the forest alone.
There are scaaary wolves in here, you know?
Where d'ya think you are going, you little shit?!
Do not you dare stand up again!
I think you have met my father before.
He was visiting your place for a checkup, so I came with him.
What the fuck are you thinkin', you little shit?!
I have seen this scene play out
It was always right in front of me.
I pretended not to see it.
And with that realization, my trembling ceased.
I have had perfect control over myself ever since.
I thought I could do anything.
One stab wound from the back and through the heart.
I told you to wait for me at the base of the mountain, did not I?
Do you have any idea what you have done?!
I put down some dangerous beasts.
They were just animals in human clothing!
Look how long the Gendarmerie took to arrive.
They would have gotten away ages ago!
You would not have made it in time!
I am criticizing you for not considering your own safety!
I wanted to save her as soon as I could.
I met you many times when you were a child.
Where do I go from here?
It is warm, is not it?
You can make your home with us.
You have experienced too much pain.
A place where only the victor survives.
We are going over the walls.
I will go assist the vanguard's retreat.
But in this world, I have found a home.
Eren, as long as you are with me,
The dream where your heart seeks comfort
Is more fragile than your life
You can abandon it, yet always find it again
In this beautiful and cruel world
Why it was we who survived
With our strength and with our weakness
If reason and logic no longer hold sway
In this world, I have found a home.
After completing her mission with the rear guard,
But the only thing awaiting her is the news of Eren's death.
